## 🚀 다음 단계

### v9.4: Weak<T> (순환 참조 방지)

```rust
use std::rc::Weak;

struct Node {
    next: RefCell<Option<Rc<Node>>>,
    prev: RefCell<Option<Weak<Node>>>,  // 순환 참조 방지
}
```

### v9.5: Arc<Mutex<T>> (멀티 스레드)

```rust
use std::sync::{Arc, Mutex};

let data = Arc::new(Mutex::new(value));
let clone = Arc::clone(&data);

std::thread::spawn(move || {
    *clone.lock().unwrap() = new_value;
});
```

